STATE
v.
Colden Aujuai COLLINS. No. 140P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2006. Amy C. Kunstling, Assistant Attorney General, Seth Edwards, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th day of March 2006 by Defendant for "Petition for Discretionary Review":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 4th day of May 2006."
